data.description: Nestled at Lees Lake, custom-built home has been meticulously crafted from the ground up. It replaced a previous structure, providing a fresh canvas for your dream dwelling. Inside, an open kitchen with an extended island and a double sink sets the stage for culinary delights. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, on the main floor, this home ensures comfort and convenience. The primary bedroom offers an oversized shower, and thoughtful touches like a pantry and a laundry room with shelves make daily life a breeze. A unique feature of this residence is the set of steps leading to additional rooms below, including a dedicated theater room for cinematic experiences and an exercise room to keep you fit and active. The main level houses a generously-sized family room, perfect for gatherings, and to the left, an additional bonus room awaits your creative touch, potentially serving as a 5th bedroom. Ascend upstairs to the loft area, and you'll discover a double closet with a bedroom to the right. The unfinished loft presents a world of customization possibilities, adding sheetrock and flooring. This amazing property not only offers a comprehensive view of the interior and exterior of the house but also includes a captivating drone video to showcase its beauty. Outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the horse and go-kart trails, walking trails, and campgrounds for hunting adventures. This property is a unique opportunity to own a custom-built haven that combines modern living with outdoor exploration.
